925
01:08:58,724 --> 01:09:02,084
Apa kabar? Hei, kau mau kemana?

926
01:09:02,212 --> 01:09:03,300
Pelan-pelan.

927
01:09:04,642 --> 01:09:07,044
Ingat kami?
- Benar.

