01:19:11,844 --> 01:19:12,932
Santai.

1064
01:19:13,060 --> 01:19:14,596
Aku tak bisa menahannya.

1065
01:19:14,724 --> 01:19:17,508
Kalian butuh ketenangan.

1066
01:19:21,091 --> 01:19:22,787
Kunyahlah ini.

